## Modification Restriction

You may not publish, redistribute, or present modified versions of the canonical documents, structure, governance model, object model, or research architecture as if they were the original or canonical material.

Modified versions must not use the project name in a way that suggests canonical status, author approval, or continuity with the original repository.

